    "description": {
      "value": "<p>You create a spectral weapon that hovers within range. It lasts for the duration.</p><p>When the weapon appears, you make a melee spell attack against a target within 5 feet of the weapon. On a hit, the target takes Force damage equal to 4d12 plus your spellcasting ability modifier.</p><p>On your later turns, you can take a Bonus Action to move the weapon up to 30 feet to a spot you can see and repeat the attack against the same target or a different one.</p>",
